'''MacBook Air'''是[[蘋果公司|蘋果公司]]（Apple）開發的超薄型[[麥金塔電腦|麥金塔]][[手提電腦|手提電腦]]系列产品，於2008年1月15日時首次發佈。蘋果公司聲稱這部電腦是「世上最薄的筆記本電腦」。<ref name="macbookair">{{cite web
  | title = MacBook Air
  | publisher = 蘋果電腦網站
  | url = http://www.apple.com/macbookair/
  | accessdate = 2011-08-14
  | archive-date = 2008-04-17
  | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080417174958/http://www.apple.com/macbookair/
  | dead-url = no
  }}</ref>

2010年10月20日，苹果发布了新款13.3寸MacBook Air。新款拥有更轻的外壳，更高分辨率的显示屏，以及更大的电池容量，并使用[[固态硬盘|固态硬盘]]取代了传统的硬盘驱动器。同时发布的还有首次被公布的11.6寸型号。MacBook Air在2011年取代停产的MacBook系列[[聚碳酸酯|聚碳酸酯]]外壳[[麥金塔笔记本电脑|麥金塔手提电脑]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.computerworld.com/s/article/9193382/Apple_s_new_11.6_in._MacBook_Air_Don_t_call_it_a_netbook |title=Apple's new 11.6-in. MacBook Air: Don't call it a netbook |accessdate=2010-11-22 |archive-date=2011-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629202037/http://www.computerworld.com/s/article/9193382/Apple_s_new_11.6_in._MacBook_Air_Don_t_call_it_a_netbook |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Apple Special Event |url=http://www.apple.com/apple-events/october-2010/ |publisher=Apple Inc. |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120421020957/http://www.apple.com/apple-events/october-2010/ |archivedate=2012-04-21 |accessdate=2010-11-22 }}</ref><ref>{{cite press release
 |url         = http://www.apple.com/pr/library/2010/10/20mba.html
 |title       = Apple Reinvents Notebooks With New MacBook Air
 |publisher   = Apple Inc.
 |deadurl     = yes
